Title: Audition Day
Plot: Liz and Pete try to rig the TGS auditions as everyone else jockeys for a chance to audition for the show or, in Tracy and Jenna's case, tries to sabotage the proceedings. Amid the chaos, Jack is treated like a pariah because of a bedbug infestation.
GuestStars: Martin Scorsese, Christopher Walken, Gilbert Gottfried, Brian Williams, Nick Fondulis
